00:26:53,070 --> 00:26:54,630
Your eyes are swollen.

582
00:26:57,810 --> 00:26:58,830
Yun Shu.

583
00:26:59,460 --> 00:27:00,840
Can I sleep here

584
00:27:00,940 --> 00:27:03,080
tonight?

585
00:27:03,170 --> 00:27:05,590
I don't want to go back
to the dormitory.

586
00:27:05,710 --> 00:27:06,910
I might die

587
00:27:06,990 --> 00:27:09,110
if I'm by myself.

588
00:27:13,430 --> 00:27:14,520
Miss Gao.

589
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:18,480
Have a glass of water.

590
00:27:20,490 --> 00:27:22,400
Can I sleep here, Mr Zhang?

591
00:27:30,820 --> 00:27:33,260
Yi Yi, I'll sleep with you tonight.

592
00:27:33,410 --> 00:27:34,430
Don't cry.

593
00:27:34,510 --> 00:27:36,570
We'll share the bad, okay?

594
00:27:36,660 --> 00:27:38,110
Drink the water.

595
00:27:39,510 --> 00:27:41,100
Your voice is hoarse.

596
00:27:59,010 --> 00:28:00,200
Yun Shu.

597
00:28:00,910 --> 00:28:03,100
How long do you think
they've been together?

598
00:28:06,540 --> 00:28:08,360
But I still think

599
00:28:08,710 --> 00:28:09,990
Lin Nuo

600
00:28:10,560 --> 00:28:12,110
wouldn't have done that.

601
00:28:12,760 --> 00:28:14,630
But that's what he did.

602
00:28:15,040 --> 00:28:16,960
He's gone too far, right?

603
00:28:25,210 --> 00:28:27,160
Yun Shu, will you sleep with me?

604
00:28:32,510 --> 00:28:34,790
Dear, I'll go back when
Yi Yi falls asleep.

605
00:28:34,890 --> 00:28:36,410
Faking sleep?

606
00:28:45,080 --> 00:28:47,280
Am I disturbing you?

607
00:28:47,620 --> 00:28:48,570
No.

608
00:28:49,210 --> 00:28:50,130
Don't say that.

609
00:28:50,220 --> 00:28:52,680
It's... It's about my work.

610
00:28:54,760 --> 00:28:55,800
Let me finish replying.

611
00:29:02,020 --> 00:29:02,720
Are you tired?

612
00:29:02,810 --> 00:29:03,690
How about

613
00:29:03,790 --> 00:29:05,030
we just go to sleep?

614
00:30:03,140 --> 00:30:04,310
Where are you going?

615
00:30:08,130 --> 00:30:10,390
I think if it's a little crowded.

616
00:30:10,490 --> 00:30:12,230
So I want to

617
00:30:12,340 --> 00:30:13,700
move to this side a little bit.

618
00:30:14,870 --> 00:30:16,460
It's not crowded.

619
00:30:18,190 --> 00:30:19,670
Okay then.

620
00:30:19,910 --> 00:30:21,800
Let's sleep.

621
00:30:50,290 --> 00:30:51,450
[Yun Shu.]

622
00:30:56,770 --> 00:30:58,910
[Okay. A moment please.]

623
00:31:37,070 --> 00:31:38,270
Yun Shu.

624
00:31:39,340 --> 00:31:40,890
There's plenty of space.

625
00:31:41,980 --> 00:31:44,300
My right arm is a little numb.

626
00:31:44,430 --> 00:31:45,720
So I sat up

627
00:31:46,430 --> 00:31:47,730
to stretch a little.

628
00:31:48,540 --> 00:31:50,040
Come here.

629
00:31:53,690 --> 00:31:54,570
Okay.

630
00:32:51,650 --> 00:32:52,529
Lan.

631
00:32:52,650 --> 00:32:53,839
Someone is here to see you.

632
00:32:54,920 --> 00:32:55,839
Who is it?

633
00:32:59,540 --> 00:33:00,500
Hello.

634
00:33:00,589 --> 00:33:01,850
I'm Lu Yu's agent.

635
00:33:01,930 --> 00:33:02,700
You can call me Xi Xi.

636
00:33:02,790 --> 00:33:04,759
Hello, I'm Yun Lan.

637
00:33:05,819 --> 00:33:06,759
Yun Lan.

638
00:33:07,270 --> 00:33:08,520
I know about

639
00:33:08,610 --> 00:33:09,750
what happened to you and Lu Yu.

640
00:33:09,840 --> 00:33:11,240
Since you're family,

641
00:33:11,360 --> 00:33:12,880
I'll cut to the chase.

642
00:33:13,760 --> 00:33:15,390
[Case file]

643
00:33:13,780 --> 00:33:14,670
Here.

644
00:33:15,410 --> 00:33:16,590
Take a look.

645
00:33:27,750 --> 00:33:31,710
[Lawyer's Letter]

646
00:33:32,230 --> 00:33:34,240
I believe you should know

647
00:33:34,770 --> 00:33:36,180
